First Department,

February, 1956

(February 7, 1956) Frieda Rader et al., Appellants, v. Manufacturers Casualty Insurance Company of Philadelphia, Penna., et al., Respondents.

Judgment unanimously affirmed, with costs. No opinion. Concur — Peck, P. J., Bastow, Rabin, Cox and Frank, JJ. [See post, p. 824.]
